<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">While fluvial processes primarily disturb the alliance, <i>Vaccinium cespitosum </i>sprouts from rhizomes following top kill from light-intensity fire. Deep duff-consuming fire kills its shallow rhizomes (Tirmenstein 1990a).</div>
